        "emailFormat": "html",
        "html": "=<p>Dear {{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json.Name }},</p>\n\n<p>Thank you for your order! We’re happy to inform you that your order has been <strong>successfully placed</strong> and is now being processed.</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p><strong>Order Details</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Order ID:</strong> {{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json['Order ID'] }}</li>\n  <li><strong>Product:</strong> {{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json['Order Itmes'] }}</li>\n  <li><strong>Payment Amount:</strong> ₹{{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json['Paid Amount'] }}</li>\n  <li><strong>Payment Mode:</strong> {{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json.Mode }}</li>\n  <li><strong>Expected Delivery Date:{{ $('Format Order Data').item.json.deliveryDate }}</strong> </li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You will receive another email once your order is delivered.</p>\n\n<p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>\n\n<p>\nBest regards,<br>\n<strong>Shri Jain Stationery Mart</strong><br>\n</p>",
        "options": {
          "attachments": "data"
        }
