        "html": "=<p>Hello Shri Jain,</p>\n\n<p>A new order has been <strong>successfully placed</strong>. Below are the order and customer details:</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p><strong>Order Information</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Order ID:</strong>{{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json[\"Order ID\"] }} </li>\n  <li><strong>Ordered Item:</strong> {{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json[\"Order Itmes\"] }}</li>\n  <li><strong>Payment Amount:</strong> ₹{{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json[\"Paid Amount\"] }}</li>\n  <li><strong>Payment Mode:</strong>{{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json.Mode }} </li>\n  <li><strong>Delivery Date:</strong> {{ $('Format Order Data').item.json['Delivery Date'] }}</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p><strong>Customer Details</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json.Name }}</li>\n  <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json.Email }}</li>\n  <li><strong>Phone:</strong>{{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json[\"Phone No.\"] }}</li>\n  <li><strong>Address:</strong><br>\n    {{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json.Address }},<br>\n{{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json.City }}– {{ $('Google Sheets Trigger').item.json[\"ZIP Code\"] }}\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Please process this order and ensure timely delivery.</p>\n\n<p>\n<strong>System Notification</strong><br>\nShri Jain Stationery Mart\n</p>",
